This is an aerial shot of Miami Beach that I took while riding in a private Cessna. Thank you very much to Juan Carlos for a beautiful and safe trip on his private plane. The flight was as fun and breathtaking as were taking these photos. We landed in Key West and stayed there for a couple of hours, then came back to Miami under the most beautiful sunset.

Esta es una vista aerea de Miami Beach tomada en avion privado donde me llevaron a los cayos de la florida. Gracias Juan Carlos por este hermoso paseo y por todas las fotografias bellas que tome durante el vuelo. Aterrizamos en Key West y estuvimos ahi por varias horas, luego regresamos a Miami donde vimos un atardecer precioso.
